      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">What it actually feels like to run a program on BreederHQ</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We have spent the page being honest about competitors. It is fair to be specific about what we are.
